    <item>
      <title>勒庞再次向巴尼耶施压，法国债券表现落后于其他债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼政党再次威胁称，如果 2025 年预算要求得不到满足，他们将推翻法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 领导的政府。法国债券因此承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/french-bonds-fall-as-le-pen-piles-pressure-on-barnier-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国 10 年期国债收益率跌至历史低位，因押注中国人民银行将放松</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/china-s-10-year-yield-is-heading-toward-record-2-on-easing-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员加大对当局将进一步放松货币政策以支撑疲软经济的押注，中国 10 年期国债收益率跌破 2% 的关键心理关口，创下历史新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/china-s-10-year-yield-is-heading-toward-record-2-on-easing-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 02:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
